e":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420131310"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420131411","id":"zettel.20260420131411","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260420131311","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":14,"offset":1327},"end":{"line":27,"column":39,"offset":1352},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420131311"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420131411","id":"zettel.20260420131411","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":3,"offset":1431},"end":{"line":31,"column":42,"offset":1470},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":72,"column":3,"offset":5819},"end":{"line":72,"column":28,"offset":5844},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420131411"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring","id":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":159,"column":3,"offset":10273},"end":{"line":159,"column":28,"offset":10298},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420131411"}],"anchors":{"gagasan":{"type":"header","text":"Gagasan","value":"gagasan","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2},"apa-itu-priming-document":{"type":"header","text":"Apa itu Priming Document","value":"apa-itu-priming-document","line":19,"column":0,"depth":2},"mengapa-ini-penting":{"type":"header","text":"Mengapa Ini Penting","value":"mengapa-ini-penting","line":30,"column":0,"depth":2},"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain":{"type":"header","text":"Hubungan ke Zettel Lain","value":"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain","line":36,"column":0,"depth":2},"sumber":{"type":"header","text":"Sumber","value":"sumber","line":42,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"priming-document-adalah-memori-stabil-level-proyek\">Priming document adalah memori stabil level proyek<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#priming-document-adalah-memori-stabil-level-proyek\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"gagasan\">Gagasan<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#gagasan\"></a></h2>\n<p>Priming document itu buat ingat aturan main proyek, bukan keputusan fitur lokal.</p>\n<h2 id=\"apa-itu-priming-document\">Apa itu Priming Document<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#apa-itu-priming-document\"></a></h2>\n<p>Priming document adalah dokumen yang menjelaskan konteks proyek yang relatif stabil dan berlaku di banyak fitur. Ini bukan daftar keputusan sesi, melainkan fondasi bersama yang membantu AI dan manusia memahami cara kerja proyek secara keseluruhan.</p>\n<p>Contoh isinya:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>stack utama: Fastify, Postgres, Redis</li>\n<li>pola arsitektur: microservice + event-driven</li>\n<li>konvensi API: snake_case di database, camelCase di klien</li>\n<li>batasan umum: hanya email di v1, tidak pakai GraphQL</li>\n<li>prinsip tim: hindari wrapper abstraksi yang tidak perlu</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"mengapa-ini-penting\">Mengapa Ini Penting<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#mengapa-ini-penting\"></a></h2>\n<p>Kalau salah ngejelasin peran ini, kita bisa salah taruh semua konteks di satu dokumen.</p>\n<p>Priming document harus stabil dan reusable. Kalau kita pakai priming document untuk semua keputusan fitur lokal, dokumen ini akan cepat usang, penuh detail sesi, dan jadi sulit dikelola. Sebaliknya, kalau kita menaruh aturan proyek di feature doc, maka aturan itu tidak dibagikan secara konsisten ke semua sesi.</p>\n<h2 id=\"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain\">Hubungan ke Zettel Lain<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#hubungan-ke-zettel-lain\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Mendukung <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.context-anchoring\">Context Anchoring — memindahkan konteks keputusan dari chat ke dokumen hidup</a> — klaim diambil dari Paragraf 14.</li>\n<li>Lihat juga <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131310\">Percakapan AI adalah medium berpikir, bukan tempat penyimpanan keputusan</a> — tesis utama bahwa chat AI adalah medium berpikir, bukan tempat penyimpanan keputusan.</li>\n<li>Lihat juga <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131311\">Kolaborasi manusia multi-hari memindahkan memori kerja ke dokumen bersama</a> — baseline kolaborasi manusia yang transfer konteks ke dokumen.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"sumber\">Sumber<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#sumber\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.context-anchoring\">Context Anchoring — memindahkan konteks keputusan dari chat ke dokumen hidup</a> — Paragraf 14</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #a03623;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.zettel\">zettel</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">ai-collaboration (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #f0944d;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.knowledge-management\">knowledge-management</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">context-anchoring (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.context-anchoring\">Context Anchoring — memindahkan konteks keputusan dari chat ke dokumen hidup</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"child